Team4450.Lib

Class LaunchPad

  • java.lang.Object
    • Team4450.Lib.LaunchPad

  • public class LaunchPad
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides an interface to the TI Launch Pad device. It monitors the state of the LP controls and raises events when control state changes and provides direct access to control status. It currently only supports buttons and rocker switches.

      • GetLatchedState

        public boolean GetLatchedState(LaunchPad.LaunchPadControlIDs requestedControl)
        For buttons, gets the latched state of a registered control. When buttons are pressed, the latch state is toggled and retained. Latched is in effect a persistent button press. Press and it latches, press again and it unlatches.
        Parameters:
        requestedControl - Control id to check.
        Returns:
        True if button latched, false if not.
